# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#   Complete Search = "Try everything, but try it SMART."
# • The art is not in trying all possibilities — it's in cutting the search tree
#   aggressively so that "all" becomes manageable.
# • Brute force + pruning = the difference between TLE and AC.
#
# 🎯 ONE LINE:
#   Backtracking = "try → recurse → undo" — the constraint prunes the tree
#
# 🔍 SIGNALS:
#   - "how to think"
#   - "visualize"
