# PROBLEM 6-1 [Easy]: Jump Game
# Problem: Array a[i] = max jump from index i. Can you reach the last index?
# Greedy: Track max reachable index. If current index > max reachable, can't proceed.
#

# ── can_jump — inline ──
# result→_cj
#
# 🎯 ONE LINE:
#   Jump game: track max reachable index greedily — O(n) single pass.
