#       FIX: use segment tree for dynamic RMQ.
#   ✗ BIT for range minimum query → BIT natively only supports prefix sums.
#       FIX: use segment tree for any RMQ with updates.
#   ✗ Lazy segment tree without push_down before recursing → stale child values.
#       FIX: push_down at the start of every update and query call.
