# ╠════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
# ║  QUERY TYPE                         → STRUCTURE                             ║
# ║  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────  ║
# ║  Static range sum                   → Prefix sum O(n) build, O(1) query    ║
# ║  Point update + range sum           → Fenwick/BIT O(log n) both             ║
# ║  Range update + range query         → Lazy segment tree O(log n) both       ║
# ║  Static range min/max               → Sparse table O(n log n) / O(1)        ║
# ║  2D range sum                       → 2D prefix sum O(nm) / O(1)            ║
