# │  ✦  Adjacency list (adj[u] = [...]) is the right default — use 90% of tim│
# │  ✦  Adjacency matrix only for n ≤ 1000 or Floyd-Warshall                 │
# │  ✦  Most hard CP problems are graph problems in disguise                 │
# │  ✦  First question: "What are the nodes? What are the edges?"            │
