# ⚠️ EDGE CASE CHECKLIST
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

#   □  Disconnected graph: run BFS/DFS from ALL unvisited nodes
#   □  Self-loops: edge (u, u) — handle in bipartite check (not a bridge)
#   □  Multi-edges: two edges between same pair — affects bridge/articulation finding
