# • Solution: LCA + DFS ordering + prefix sums.
#
# • PROBLEM 14-4 [Very Hard]: Heavy-Light Decomposition Decompose tree into chains.
# • Range queries on paths reduce to segment tree queries.
# • Advanced technique for Div.1 C/D problems.
