# ╠════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
# ║  SPANNING TREE NEED                 → ALGORITHM                             ║
# ║  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────  ║
# ║  Minimum spanning tree              → Kruskal (sort edges) or Prim (heap)   ║
# ║  Kruskal vs Prim                    → Sparse: Kruskal; Dense: Prim O(V²)    ║
# ║  Connected components               → Union-Find                            ║
# ║  Detect cycle (undirected)          → Union-Find: find(u)==find(v) before add║
# ║  Maximum spanning tree              → Kruskal with edges sorted descending  ║
