#   1. Run DFS, record finish times (Kosaraju) or track low-links (Tarjan)
#   2. Kosaraju: transpose the graph, DFS again in reverse finish-time order
#   3. Each DFS tree in pass 2 (Kosaraju) or each completed node in Tarjan = one SCC
#   → Kosaraju = 2 DFS passes; Tarjan = 1 DFS — both O(V+E)
