#   □  Single node with self-loop → SCC of size 1, node is in its own SCC.
#   □  All nodes mutually reachable → 1 SCC (the whole graph).
#   □  Directed path (no back edges) → each node is its own SCC (n SCCs).
#   □  2-SAT: variable forced TRUE → add_clause(i, False, i, False) (xi OR xi → xi must be true).
#   □  2-SAT: variable forced FALSE → add_clause(i, True, i, True) (¬xi OR ¬xi).
#   □  After Kosaraju: SCC IDs are 1-indexed from condensation perspective.
