#   │ Trial division               │ O(√n)           │ Factorize single number  │
#   │ GCD (Euclidean)              │ O(log min(a,b)) │ Python: math.gcd         │
#   │ Fast exponentiation          │ O(log k)        │ pow(a,k,mod) built-in    │
#   │ Modular inverse (Fermat)     │ O(log p)        │ Only for prime modulus   │
#   │ Miller-Rabin                 │ O(k log² n)     │ k = number of witnesses  │
#   └──────────────────────────────┴─────────────────┴──────────────────────────┘
