# ▶ 26F. LYNDON FACTORIZATION — DUVAL'S ALGORITHM
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# 🎯 ONE LINE:
#   String hashing: rolling hash enables O(1) substring comparison after O(n) preprocessing
#
# 🔍 SIGNALS:
#   - "longest prefix match"
