#   - "minimum days"
#   - "fewest operations"
#   - "binary search on answer"
#   - "parametric search"
#
# ❌ MISTAKES:
#   ✗ Searching on array indices when you should search on answer values
#   ✗ check(mid) function is O(n²) making total O(n² log n) — optimize check() first
#
#
# 🧠 THINKING:
#   1. What does brute force look like?
#   2. What is the complexity bottleneck?
#   3. What structure or property enables optimization?
#   → Code the optimized approach
