# │  P   │ Lucas' Theorem nCr mod small prime       │ O(p + log_p n) │ 1800-2│
# │  Q   │ Tonelli-Shanks modular sqrt              │ O(log² p)      │ 2000-2│
# │  R   │ Stars and Bars                           │ O(1)           │ 1200-1│
