# │  R   │ Stirling Numbers 2nd Kind               │ O(n²)          │ 1900-26│
# │  S   │ Burnside's Lemma (necklace/bracelet)     │ O(n log n)     │ 2000-2│
# │  T   │ Möbius Sieve (linear)                    │ O(n)           │ 1900-2│
# │  T   │ Euler φ sieve (linear)                   │ O(n)           │ 1600-2│
# │  U   │ Sum of GCD(i,n) for i=1..n               │ O(sqrt n)      │ 1600-2│
